p:
The overall potential of agro-processing of 
 Mimusops zeyheri is huge as it is capable of: 


   (a)

Increasing the value of the output of poor farmers thus, higher returns and improved livelihood;


   (b)

Expanding market opportunities for the farmers;


   (c)

Extending the shelf-life and improving the palatability of the fruit;


   (d)

Increasing diversity of value-added products;


   (e)

Enhancing food security by reducing food losses while increasing availability and accessibility;


   (f)

Overcoming seasonality and perishability constraints; and


   (g)

Empowering women who are often more involved in agro-processing activities than men.
